  </view>

  <view class="intro-section">
    <view class="intro-card">
      <text class="intro-card-text">项目紧扣农业农村现代化战略，聚焦陕南安康富硒茯茶产业痛点，以智能化发花技术为核心，研发金花智控设备，打造"智能装备+标准工艺+数字平台+品牌赋能"一体化方案，破解产业瓶颈，赋能茶农增收与区域特色经济高质量发展。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">🎯 核心痛点</view>
  <view class="pain-point-list">
    <view class="pain-item">
      <view class="pain-icon">⚠️</view>
      <view class="pain-content">
        <text class="pain-title">品质不稳定</text>
        <text class="pain-desc">传统发花依赖人工，品质与金花密度不稳</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="pain-item">
      <view class="pain-icon">⚠️</view>
      <view class="pain-content">
        <text class="pain-title">分拣效率低</text>
        <text class="pain-desc">人工分拣低效粗糙，原料浪费严重</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="pain-item">
      <view class="pain-icon">⚠️</view>
      <view class="pain-content">
        <text class="pain-title">硒含量不均</text>
        <text class="pain-desc">温湿度失控致硒含量不均，产品附加值低</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

